title: Episode 231: Live Tour Detroit (Feat. Comic J Will, Sada Baby & Icewear Vezzo)
itunes:title: Episode 231: Live Tour Detroit (Feat. Comic J Will, Sada Baby & Icewear Vezzo)
description:
Shouts to everyone who came to our SOLD OUT show in Detroit. Comic J Will, Sada Baby, and Icewear Vezzo joined the ladies of Lip Service and things got wild. Comic J Will opens up about the time he had an allergic reaction to bigen (hair dye), manscaping and more. Sada baby and Icewear Vezzo were basically battling the ladies all night. Enjoy!
